00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:26,240
Well, you gotta pick the one
you love the best

575
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:28,600
because you only get married once.

576
00:36:32,680 --> 00:36:35,600
Oh, my gosh, I love this one.

577
00:36:35,720 --> 00:36:38,440
