658
00:41:31,080 --> 00:41:33,300
but I don't have a choice.

659
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:38,540
Oh, Mom, you can pretend all you want,
that nothing has changed. But I have.

660
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:42,740
