00:41:57,680 --> 00:41:59,900
And be proud of myself.

666
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:03,400
Don't you want me
to be that person anymore?

667
00:42:09,360 --> 00:42:13,800
The lying is over. You and Dad are gonna
