719
00:46:37,800 --> 00:46:40,300
If you don't want to, it's okay but...

720
00:46:40,400 --> 00:46:42,840
it would mean a lot to me if you would.

721
00:46:45,280 --> 00:46:48,600
- You want me to be your maid of honor?
